27/06/2006
ANKARA, Turkey -- European Commission Ambassador to Turkey Hansjorg Kretschmer is warning a newly established political formation, the Party of Democratic Society, over apparent links to the outlawed Kurdistan Workers' Party. 
Speaking Monday (26 June), Kretschmer said any formation willing to participate in politics must firmly differentiate itself from terrorism. 
(Milliyet - 27/06/06; Hurriyet - 26/06/06)
